tools.description:
Retrieve seller or broker information by seller_id.

Args:
    seller_id (str): The unique ID of the seller or broker.

Returns:
    dict: {
        "success": True,
        "data": {
            "seller_id": str,
            "name": str,
            "contact_info": str,
            "agency": str
        }
    }
    or
    {
        "success": False,
        "error": str  # e.g., "Seller not found"
    }

Constraints:
    - The seller/broker with the given seller_id must exist in the system.
